Magnemite (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0080: Slowbro
Pokémon
#0082: Magneton →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Magnemite (TCG Pocket).

Magnemite has been featured on 42 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Magnemite cards are normally Lightning-type or Metal-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Magnemite

Magnemite
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
